      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 15:45:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨呼吁美国尊重边界不可侵犯性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/scholz-calls-on-the-us-to-respect-the-inviolability-of-borders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨反驳了美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的言论，包括威胁使用经济力量吞并加拿大和夺取格陵兰岛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/scholz-calls-on-the-us-to-respect-the-inviolability-of-borders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 15:45:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大财政部长勒布朗表示不会竞选自由党领袖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/canada-finance-minister-leblanc-says-he-won-t-run-for-liberal-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大财政部长多米尼克·勒布朗 (Dominic LeBlanc) 决定不竞选自由党领袖，称他需要专注于应对唐纳德·特朗普政府的关税威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/canada-finance-minister-leblanc-says-he-won-t-run-for-liberal-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 15:25:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
