      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 15:02:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗加大委内瑞拉镇压力度 引发邻国谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/maduro-ratchets-up-repression-ahead-of-inauguration-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派计划在全国范围内发起抗议活动，谴责尼古拉斯·马杜罗本周就任总统，委内瑞拉政府因此发动新一轮镇压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/maduro-ratchets-up-repression-ahead-of-inauguration-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在税收斗争前召集关注 SALT 的共和党人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-calls-salt-focused-republicans-to-florida-before-tax-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有关延长 2017 年减税政策的斗争即将爆发之前，来自纽约、新泽西和加利福尼亚州的约 20 名共和党众议院议员应邀于周六在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的海湖庄园与他会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-calls-salt-focused-republicans-to-florida-before-tax-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 21:26:27 GMT</pubDate>
